description: Stepbrothers Carter Woods and Hoss Kado get back from baseball practice to find the parents away and more than just time on their hands. As they eagerly wash away the dirt from practice, these two smokin' stepbrothers can't resist pleasuring each other's toned, rippling bodies. With the house to themselves, they've got the time to stroke, suck, and pound their way to a sticky mess of their own. It's no wonder Carter is Hoss's favorite catcher. Enjoy!
title: My Stepbrother's Favorite Catcher
